outline:
1. to give, provide
    1. (P'al)
      1. to give
      2. to place, lay (foundations)
    2. (Hithp'al)
      1. to be given
      2. to be paid
kjv_def: deliver, give, lay, [phrase] prolong, pay, yield.
strongs_def: {to give (whether literal or figurative); generally, to put; imperatively (reflexive) come}
